  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645460/extras/8e020322ea82e94e22ca02f57af136b5.webp?t=1760137431\" width=722 height=7 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIND MAZE - is a logical competitive game based on capturing of the playing field.</h2><br>Put a walls, build a labyrinth, capture cells of playing field. Do not let the appearance of closed corners to avoid being captured by enemy.<br><br>Calculate the moves to build a strategy, create a logical trap for opponent. Be cunning, force your opponent to make a mistake and cover the field like rapid avalanche, carrying you to victory.<br><br>Play the single-player campaign or compete with players online.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Win and get the championship of the leaderboard!</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645460/extras/8e020322ea82e94e22ca02f57af136b5.webp?t=1760137431\" width=722 height=7 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645460/extras/ed6974548be67c128563b8f8bccc019b.webp?t=1760137431\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645460/extras/8e020322ea82e94e22ca02f57af136b5.webp?t=1760137431\" width=722 height=7 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645460/extras/8e020322ea82e94e22ca02f57af136b5.webp?t=1760137431\" width=722 height=7 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIND MAZE - is a logical competitive game based on capturing of the playing field.</h2><br>Put a walls, build a labyrinth, capture cells of playing field. Do not let the appearance of closed corners to avoid being captured by enemy.<br><br>Calculate the moves to build a strategy, create a logical trap for opponent. Be cunning, force your opponent to make a mistake and cover the field like rapid avalanche, carrying you to victory.<br><br>Play the single-player campaign or compete with players online.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Win and get the championship of the leaderboard!</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645460/extras/8e020322ea82e94e22ca02f57af136b5.webp?t=1760137431\" width=722 height=7 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645460/extras/ed6974548be67c128563b8f8bccc019b.webp?t=1760137431\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/645460/extras/8e020322ea82e94e22ca02f57af136b5.webp?t=1760137431\" width=722 height=7 /></span>",
